	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ты угадал<gender2 m="" f="а" />! Это <tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" />!<delay frames="40" />
Молодчина, козявка! <tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="6" />!</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ай, какая досада! <delay20 />Это <tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" />!<delay frames="40" />
